  "prompt": "What should I search in Quora?",
  "response": "When searching on Quora, consider looking for information or advice on topics that interest you or that you have questions about. Here are some ideas to help you get started:\n\n1. **Personal Development**: Questions about improving productivity, building habits, or managing time.\n   - \"How can I stay motivated to achieve my goals?\"\n   - \"What are the best books for personal growth?\"\n\n2. **Career and Professional Advice**: Insights on job searching, career changes, or workplace skills.\n   - \"How do I prepare for a job interview in tech?\"\n   - \"What are the most in-demand skills for 2023?\"\n\n3. **Health and Wellness**: Tips on physical and mental health, fitness, or nutrition.\n   - \"What are some effective ways to reduce stress?\"\n   - \"How can I start a healthy eating routine?\"\n\n4. **Technology**: Updates, tutorials, or troubleshooting related to tech.\n   - \"What are the best AI tools for content creation?\"\n   - \"How do I choose between Android and iPhone?\"\n\n5. **Travel and Lifestyle**: Recommendations for destinations, travel tips, or lifestyle hacks.\n   - \"What are the top things to do in Bali?\"\n   - \"How can I pack efficiently for a long trip?\"\n\n6. **Education and Learning**: Resources for studying, learning new skills, or choosing courses.\n   - \"What are the best free online courses for coding?\"\n   - \"How can I improve my language learning skills?\"\n\n7. **Relationships and Social Life**: Advice on friendships, dating, or family dynamics.\n   - \"How can I maintain long-distance friendships?\"\n   - \"What are the signs of a healthy relationship?\"\n\n8. **Finance and Investing**: Tips on saving, budgeting, or investing wisely.\n   - \"What are the best ways to save money on a tight budget?\"\n   - \"How do I start investing in the stock market?\"\n\n9. **Hobbies and Interests**: Ideas for pursuing hobbies or exploring new interests.\n   - \"What are some beginner-friendly photography tips?\"\n   - \"How can I start a gardening project at home?\"\n\n10. **Current Events and Trends**: Discussions on news, trends, or societal issues.\n    - \"What are the implications of AI on the job market?\"\n    - \"How is climate change affecting our daily lives?\"\n\nTo make the most of Quora:\n- Use **specific keywords** to find relevant answers.\n- Explore **spaces** (topic-based communities) for curated content.\n- Follow topics or people who share expertise in areas you're interested in.\n- Engage by **asking questions** or **upvoting** helpful answers.\n\nLet me know if you'd like help crafting a specific query!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
